<p>Champions of Balance pg. 21 <InnerLink id="backlink-ability-arcane_discoveries-ref-D-1" data-hash-target to="ability-arcane_discoveries-ref-D-1" aria-label="Back to reference D-1">↩</InnerLink> <InnerLink id="backlink-ability-arcane_discoveries-ref-D-2" data-hash-target to="ability-arcane_discoveries-ref-D-2" aria-label="Back to reference D-2">↩<sup>2</sup></InnerLink> <InnerLink id="backlink-ability-arcane_discoveries-ref-D-3" data-hash-target to="ability-arcane_discoveries-ref-D-3" aria-label="Back to reference D-3">↩<sup>3</sup></InnerLink> <InnerLink id="backlink-ability-arcane_discoveries-ref-D-4" data-hash-target to="ability-arcane_discoveries-ref-D-4" aria-label="Back to reference D-4">↩<sup>4</sup></InnerLink></p>
